result.notes:
Analysis of samples collected on a plankton survey to assess distribution of 
fish eggs and larvae in the southern North Sea and eastern English Channel. 
Numbers of ichthyoplankton from main net samples, zooplankton from fine mesh 
and water samples, and associated positional data and volumes filtered.
